11 An act relating to prohibiting certain artificial dyes in foods and beverages
12 served or sold at school
13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. 16 V.S.A. § 1264b is added to read:
15 § 1264b. ARTIFICIAL DYES
16 (a) In operating its school lunch and breakfast program, pursuant to the
17 National School Lunch Act, as amended, and the Child Nutrition Act, as
18 amended, respectively, or selling competitive food, a school district and an
19 approved independent school shall not serve a food or beverage during the
20 school day containing one or more of the following substances:
