1 (1) Blue 1 (CAS 3844-45-9);
2 (2) Blue 2 (CAS 860-22-0);
3 (3) Green 3 (CAS 2353-45-9);
4 (4) Red 40 (CAS 25956-17-6);
5 (5) Yellow 5 (CAS 1934-21-0); and
6 (6) Yellow 6 (CAS 2783-94-0).
7 (b) Subsection (a) of this section shall not apply to those foods or
8 beverages sold or served away from a school campus or at least one half-hour
9 after the school day until 12:00 midnight.
10 (c) As used in this section:
11 (1) “Competitive food” has the same meaning as in 7 C.F.R. § 210.11.
12 (2) “School day,” as pertains to public schools, shall be defined by the
13 school district pursuant to subsection 1071(b) of this title, and as pertains to
14 approved independent schools, means the hours fixed by a school for
15 instruction each day.
16 Sec. 2. EFFECTIVE DATE
17 This act shall take effect on July 1, 2027.
